text: Joanna Cassidy (born Joanna Victoria Caskey, August 2, 1945 in Haddonfield, New Jersey) is an American actress. She acted in the TV series Six Feet Under and Body of Proof. She acted in many movies. These include Blade Runner (1982), Where the Heart Is and Who Framed Roger Rabbit?. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from New Jersey Category:1945 births Category:Living people
